  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to libqmi</title>

    <para>
      The <application>libqmi</application> is a glib-based library for talking to WWAN modems and devices which speak the 
      Qualcomm MSM Interface (QMI) protocol.
    </para>

    &lfs75_checked;

